runtime/logs/codex-patlas-exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit-step-001-explorer-001.log:1849:/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:5:This branch is only live after one stable notion of a near-closed Tao circuit has been fixed. Given that frozen object, the question is whether exact Navier-Stokes forces a uniformly nontrivial off-circuit transfer on an explicit packet class, or whether an adversarial family can drive that transfer to zero while preserving the intended Tao-role logic over a stated activation window.
